eCommerce

Build responsive online stores set up to sell anything, anywhere. Customize the design of product pages, sort catalogs with dynamic categories, offer an optimized checkout—and leverage open platform capabilities and APIs to meet specific business needs.

Learn more

Bookings

Set up an online scheduling system where business runs like clockwork—with built-in capabilities to take bookings and payments, customize schedules and manage staff, create one-time or recurring pricing plans for services and more.

Events

Create any in-person or online event, customize the event page and invites and design seating maps. Sell tickets or collect RSVPs, keep track of guest lists and boost attendance with built-in marketing tools.

Restaurants

Build restaurant sites with a robust online ordering and reservation system built-in. Design custom menus and reach customers with automated marketing campaigns, gift cards, loyalty programs and more.

Blog

Boost SEO and build online communities by adding blogs to sites. Assign roles to multiple writers, use tags and categories to sort by topic, monetize with subscription pricing plans and more.

Multilingual

Set sites up for international growth so they can reach customers and rank in search results in different geos. Translate sites into over 180 languages manually or automatically—while keeping the design intact.

Payments

Safeguard both site owners and customers with a secure payment solution. Accept all major payment methods like debit and credit cards or Apple Pay, add shipping and tax—or offer the option to pay in installments.

Pricing Plans

Create custom pricing plans to sell packages, memberships and subscriptions. Charge visitors once-off or recurring payments for exclusive content or services, connect various payment methods and add discounts.

Members Area

Build a community around sites to engage customers and keep them coming back. Let visitors create their own account, keep track of their orders and wishlist and access exclusive content.

CRM

Convert more leads with built-in CRM tools—from collecting contact info with custom forms to adding live chat. Plus, organize projects and funnels, assign tasks to teams and reply to messages from all channels in one inbox.

Hotels

Build and run hospitality businesses with Wix Hotels by HotelRunner. Manage availability and reservations from one place, offer guests custom packages and connect to leading platforms like Booking.com, Airbnb and Expedia to maximize occupancy.

App Builder

Build fully-branded mobile apps that integrate seamlessly with a site, or as a standalone solution. Customize every part of the look and layout, add the content and features you need and get it listed on the App Store and Google Play.

Bring on the integrations

Connect industry-leading platforms and add any functionality with 500+ apps to fit any business needs.

Browse the App Market

Build beyond the platform

Crack any project with code

Build on your terms, from backend to frontend. Extend the logic and functionality with 100s of Wix-made or third-party APIs and integrations.

Take our business solutions anywhere

Learn more

Custom solutions for big brands
